		<title>How To Grow Your Fiction Email List Subscribers. My Own Case Study</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheCreativePenn/~3/poVqsB7gBfc/</link>
		<comments>http://www.thecreativepenn.com/2015/01/15/fiction-email-list-subscribers/#comments</comments>
